{{common_mistakes}}

Step {{current_step}} completed successfully.

Evidence: {{evidence}}

1. Record step result
2. Increment counter: current_step = {{current_step}} + 1, step_retry = 0
3. {{#if has_file_access}}Read next step data from file {{workspace_path}}/plan.md and fill current_step_action and current_step_expected_output.{{else}}Find step with id = ({{current_step}} + 1) in steps array and fill current_step_action (its action) and current_step_expected_output (its expected_output). If no next step - leave empty.{{/if}}
4. Update execution_note to: "{{task_short_name}}. Step ({{current_step}}+1)/{{total_steps}}"

Step {{current_step}} skipped.

Reason: {{ask-user-skip-or-escalate.skip_reason}}

